      <title>Starmer面临夏季的劳动起义，并要求征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/starmer-faces-summer-of-labour-revolts-and-calls-for-taxing-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯尔·斯泰默（Keir Starmer）在他的工党中面临政治家的越来越大的压力，以对英国经济采取更大胆的态度，从而为公共服务提供了更加重大的改进。他们的解决方案？提高税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/starmer-faces-summer-of-labour-revolts-and-calls-for-taxing-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国顶级疫苗官员辞职，认为RFK“错误信息”推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/top-us-vaccine-official-resigns-citing-rfk-misinformation-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社（Bloomberg）收到的一封信，食品和药物管理局的顶级疫苗监管机构周五突然辞职，理由是他所谓的健康和公共服务部长罗伯特·肯尼迪（Robert F. Kennedy Jr.]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/top-us-vaccine-official-resigns-citing-rfk-misinformation-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 02:16:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
