      <title>韩国前总统月亮召唤询问：yonhap</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/south-korea-ex-president-moon-summoned-for-questioning-yonhap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yonhap报道说，韩国当局已召集前总统Joae-In提出讯问，这是对与他的前妇女任命在泰国航空公司任命有关的贿赂指控的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/south-korea-ex-president-moon-summoned-for-questioning-yonhap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 00:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
